Name: Ansiolisis
About the game: Ansiolisis (or Anxiolysis) is a short interactive narrative text-based adventure over a dream of someone with anxiety. 'A short history about falling', the game consists on a series of passages, narratives and poems with an unsetting atmospheric ost, to uncover (and relate) to the situation of falling and anxiety
